description:
.NET Compilers Toolset Package.
      Referencing this package will cause the project to be built using the C# and Visual Basic compilers contained in the package, as opposed to the version installed with MSBuild.

      This package is primarily intended to establish a develop environment for developing Qtyi .NET Compiler Platform ("Luna").

      This package also support scenarios that need to access internal types and members in assemblies from other third-parties.

      This package requires either MSBuild 16.3 and .NET Desktop 4.7.2+ or .NET Core 2.1+

      
    
      More details at https://aka.ms/roslyn-packages
      This package was built from the source at https://github.com/qtyi/roslyn.git/commit/d90f754622ca88ae56eb5a31903abc71afe0e5f6.
